text: Faresene nobed mang始eny miwuoro mi buru ma tiendegi dhwolo ka giringo noumi. Ohinga magi noyiengni kowinjo koko mag farese mag lweny gi geche man-gi tiende ariyo mag lweny kod geche moum wigi man-gi tiende ang始wen, chieng始 ma enodonj gie dhorangeyeni kaka ji donjo e dala maduong始 ma ohinga mare osenyon mopiel piny.
